        html: '<div class="kg-card-markdown"><p>[C\u1eadp nh\u1eadt m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 thay \u0111\u1ed5i v\u1ec1 L\u1ecaCH HO\u1ea0T \u0110\u1ed8NG T\u1ebeT t\u1ea1i 2 khu v\u1ef1c Tp. H\u1ed3 Ch\u00ed Minh v\u00e0 H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i t\u1eeb ng\u00e0y 11/02/2021]<br>\nT\u1ebft n\u00e0y m\u00ecnh c\u00e0 ph\u00ea nh\u00e9!<br>\nNh\u00e0 g\u1eedi b\u1ea1n th\u00f4ng b\u00e1o l\u1ecbch ho\u1ea1t \u0111\u1ed9ng T\u1ebft c\u1ee7a 177 c\u1eeda h\u00e0ng tr\u00ean to\u00e0n qu\u1ed1c.<br>\nB\u00e1nh ngon, b\u1ed9 \u0111\u00f4i D\u01b0a l\u01b0\u1edbi thanh m\u00e1t, s\u00f4 c\u00f4 la g\u1eebng ng\u1ecdt ng\u00e0o, l\u1eabn g\u00f3c b\u00e0n quen thu\u1ed9c - \u0111\u1ec1u \u0111\u00e3 s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng c\u00f9ng team m\u00ecnh \u0111\u00f3n 1 m\u00f9a T\u1ebft h\u00ean, kho\u1ebb v\u00e0 sum v\u1ea7y r\u1ed3i \u0111\u1ea5y, gh\u00e9 Nh\u00e0 g\u1ea7n nh\u1ea5t m\u00ecnh c\u00e0 ph\u00ea nh\u00e9!<br>\n<img src="/content/images/2021/02/CH_MN1.jpg" alt="CH_MN1"><br>\n<img src="/content/images/2021/02/CH_MN2.jpg" alt="CH_MN2"><br>\n<img src="/content/images/2021/02/CH_MN3.jpg" alt="CH_MN3"><br>\n<img src="/content/images/2021/02/CH_MN4.jpg" alt="CH_MN4"><br>\n<img src="/content/images/2021/02/CH_MN5.jpg" alt="CH_MN5"><br>\n<img src="/content/images/2021/02/CH_MN6.jpg" alt="CH_MN6"><br>\n<img src="/content/images/2021/02/CH_MN7.jpg" alt="CH_MN7"><br>\n<img src="/content/images/2021/02/CH_MN8.jpg" alt="CH_MN8"><br>\n<img src="/content/images/2021/02/CH_MN-khac.jpg" alt="CH_MN-khac"><br>\n<img src="/content/images/2021/02/CH_MN-khac2.jpg" alt="CH_MN-khac2"><br>\n<img src="/content/images/2021/02/CH_MT.jpg" alt="CH_MT"><br>\n<img src="/content/images/2021/02/CH_MT2.jpg" alt="CH_MT2"><br>\n<img src="/content/images/2021/02/CH_HN1.jpg" alt="CH_HN1"><br>\n<img src="/content/images/2021/02/CH_HN2.jpg" alt="CH_HN2"><br>\n<img src="/content/images/2021/02/CH_HN3.jpg" alt="CH_HN3"><br>\n<img src="/content/images/2021/02/CH_HN4.jpg" alt="CH_HN4"><br>\n<img src="/content/images/2021/02/CH_MB.jpg" alt="CH_MB"></p>\n<hr>\n<p>V\u00e0 b\u1ea1n \u01a1i, vui T\u1ebft nh\u01b0ng \u0111\u1eebng qu\u00ean n\u00e2ng cao tinh th\u1ea7n ch\u1ee7 \u0111\u1ed9ng b\u1ea3o v\u1ec7 s\u1ee9c kho\u1ebb b\u1ea3n th\u00e2n v\u00e0 c\u1ed9ng \u0111\u1ed3ng b\u1eb1ng c\u00e1ch \u0111eo kh\u1ea9u trang, th\u01b0\u1eddng xuy\u00ean r\u1eeda tay nh\u00e9! Nh\u00e0 g\u1ea7n b\u1ea1n c\u0169ng \u0111\u00e3:</p>\n<ul>\n<li>Chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb n\u01b0\u1edbc r\u1eeda tay t\u1ea1i qu\u1ea7y cho kh\u00e1ch h\u00e0ng.</li>\n<li>\u0110\u1ea3m b\u1ea3o 100% nh\u00e2n vi\u00ean \u0111eo kh\u1ea9u trang, r\u1eeda tay 30 ph\u00fat 1 l\u1ea7n trong su\u1ed1t th\u1eddi gian ph\u1ee5c v\u1ee5.</li>\n<li>V\u00e0 \u0111\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t theo ch\u1ec9 th\u1ecb c\u1ee7a th\u00e0nh ph\u1ed1 - t\u1ea1i 1 s\u1ed1 t\u1ec9nh th\u00e0nh, Nh\u00e0 xin ph\u00e9p ph\u1ee5c v\u1ee5 v\u1edbi s\u1ed1 l\u01b0\u1ee3ng kh\u00e1ch c\u00f3 h\u1ea1n b\u1ea1n nh\u00e9!</li>\n</ul>\n</div>',
